high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black round table on the left.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the middle of the table.
Turn around and walk to the white fridge.
Put the head of lettuce inside the fridge on the left shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the right side inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce inside a sink.

high_descs: Turn around, walk left around the table to the opposite side.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the table.
Turn around and walk a bit right to the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge on the bottom shelf, left side. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn right and walk along the counter to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the right sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the fridge then turn left and take two steps then turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the lettuce that's in front of you.
Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the counter then turn left.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right then take a step to your right then walk to the sink and turn left to face the sink.
Put the lettuce in the right sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold head of lettuce in the sink.
